dct_title_s: Course of the river Mississippi, from the Balise to Fort Chartres taken on an expedition to the Illinois, in the latter end of the year 1765
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Prime meridian: New Orleans and Ferro. Shows historic points of interest. Includes descriptive notes and "Depths of the Mississippi."
